+# BANK 071: Battle Data
+
+Battle enemy templates and encounter tables are stored in ROM bank 7.
+
+```text
+bank 2: messages
+bank 3: sprites / map graphics
+bank 4: map data
+bank 6: font data
+bank 7: battle data
+```
+
+The runtime wrapper copies enemy data into WRAM before the battle starts.
