+/*
+ * ============================================================================
+ * GBDK RPG GRAPHICS SAFETY CHECKPOINT (rpg030)
+ * ============================================================================
+ *
+ * This project previously white-screened when graphics were expanded too quickly.
+ * The boot path is:
+ *
+ *   main()
+ *     -> dialogue_init()
+ *     -> init_game()
+ *     -> load_map_mode()
+ *          -> DISPLAY_OFF
+ *          -> snap_camera_to_player()
+ *          -> draw_object_map()
