++/* GRAPHICS HOTSPOT: draw_object_map()
++ *
++ * Responsibilities:
++ * - Convert current area's 16x16 object map into the 32x32 BG buffer.
++ * - Apply visual-only BG overlays such as forest markers.
++ * - Upload BG tile data and BG map data.
